{
  "stem": "888.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't think-- even if you weren't Jewish and they threw a stone at you, I don't think they were too sorry, either.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, you know, call you dirty Jews and all kind of, all kind of--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I mean-- the synagogue, they were discussing, I mean, different events, you know, that happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, like for instance, in Romania at that particular time when they had the Iron Guard and so on and so forth, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was different cities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where there was a pogrom or something, you know, or they, you know, ganged up, or they desecrated a temple, or something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was always, you know, a conversation, in the-- you know, in the mikveh, mainly-- mikveh or in the temple, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean by making--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Romania wasn't as bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Romania, it started, I remember, when King Carol, you know, abdicated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his son came, you know, and then the Iron Guard, you know, and then these different things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, our city wasn't as-- how shall I say?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, we weren't as involved because the population was more different population.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like Germans, and Hungarian, and Serbs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, it was more of a mixture of population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But places where it was, you know, populated or predominantly Hungarian or predominantly Romanian, of course, the Romanians in their country felt, you know, stronger.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these things was happening, you know, quite often.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for a while it was OK, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, of course, you know, even though-- like for instance, our home town was a military town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there was quite a few-- [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
